 ## CI Bots
 
 - PR Verify bot: runs lint/type/tests + toy eval, fails on ECE regression.
 - Triage bot: auto-labels issues/PRs, welcomes first-time contributors.
+
+### Providers Smoke (latency & availability)
+
+We run a tiny matrix job that exercises **stub**, **OpenAI**, and **Anthropic** adapters (if keys are present) and publishes:
+
+- p50/p95 latency per provider
+- which providers ran vs. were skipped
+- cache stats (entries/bytes)
+
+Artifacts:
+
+- `benchmarks/smoke/providers.json`
+- `benchmarks/smoke/summary.md`
+
+Secrets required to hit real providers:
+
+- `OPENAI_API_KEY`
+- `ANTHROPIC_API_KEY`
